(1256, '_transient_dash_c05853b002c443ec8e57ff884f56cdde', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://es.wordpress.org/2016/03/25/wordpress-4-5-candidata-a-definitiva/''>WordPress 4.5 candidata a definitiva</a> <span class="rss-date">25 marzo, 2016</span><div class="rssSummary">La versión candidata a definitiva de WordPress 4.5 ya está disponible. Hemos realizado 49 cambios desde la Beta 4 de hace una semana. RC (candidata a definitiva) significa que ya lo hemos  logrado, pero que con millones de usuarios y miles de plugins y temas es posible que se nos haya pasado algo. Esperamos lanzar WordPress 4.5 [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/in-case-you-missed-it-issue-6''>WPTavern: In Case You Missed It – Issue 6</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/features-as-plugins-first-transitions-into-features-as-projects''>WPTavern: Features-as-Plugins First Transitions Into Features-as-Projects</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/bbpress-2-6-expected-later-this-year-two-major-features-pushed-back-to-2-7''>WPTavern: bbPress 2.6 Expected Later This Year, Two Major Features Pushed Back to 2.7</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Plugin popular:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Page Builder by SiteOrigin</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=siteorigin-panels&amp;_wpnonce=63a1d71b5c&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Page Builder by SiteOrigin''>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no');
